snippet.title: Attack of the Mutant Artificial Trees (Windows game 2004)
snippet.description:
Attack of the Mutant Artificial Trees is a simple shooting game by Blockdot, KewlBox, National Christmas Tree Association.
The object is to hit as many of the mutant artificial trees in a 30 second round as possible.
